<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l23">ſach voꝛ ew mit dem rechten cʒuhandeln hab von ſchulde wegen / die Jr Merckel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l24">hübel <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> Arman ſchuldig ſeÿ / 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> er <expan>heinriche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> ſun hinauf ſende </del> / als </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l25">
<add><ab facs="#facs_129_r1l26">ſie </ab></add> euch 
<del rend="strikethrough"> der </del> ſelber 
<del rend="strikethrough"> ſein ſun </del> wol ercʒeln wirt / <expan>Rog<ex>amus</ex></expan> daʒ Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">Jm </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_129_line_1575358167665_373"><expan>derſelbe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>B<ex>urgerin</ex></expan> </ab></add> cʒum <expan>rechte<ex>n</ex></expan> fürder </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l27">lichen vnd beholffen ſein wöllet / durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen / daʒ Jr dieſelbe Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_129_r1l28">
<del rend="strikethrough">ſein </del> ſchüld von dem <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gericht vnd beʒalt vverde / <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnu<ex>er</ex>tʒoge<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
